Inspetor has a standardized format for accepting payment information that is associated with a sale. You can find the accepted and required parameters below:

Property             | When is it required?   | Type    | Description
--------             | ---------------------  | ----    | -----------
**method**           | `POST`                 | String  | The method of payment being used. *The allowed values are `credit_card`, `boleto`, and `other`*
**installments**     | `POST`                 | Integer | The number of "*parcelas*" that the user will pay
**first_six_digits** | `POST`                 | String  | The first six digits of the credit card number
**last_four_digits** | `POST`                 | Integer | The last four digits of the credit card number
**holder_name**      | `POST`                 | String  | The full name of the owner of the credit card
**holder_cpf**       | `POST`                 | String  | The CPF of the owner of the credit card
**billing_address**  | `POST`                 | [InspetorAddress](#inspetoraddress) | The billing address associated with this credit card